g vil forby salg av all snus innen mars 2013. Sverige er det eneste EU-landet som har en egen avtale om fritak fra totalforbudet i unionen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "sport"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "sport|sprek"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5a2ee8d5b0d0152274ef481af07ca78223ba592b087ba35b552eaf697e8c723c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-10-27T19:36:04.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Snus kan redusere utholdenheten og \u00f8ker skaderisikoen ved trening. Likevel legger 420 000 nordmenn daglig en pris under leppa."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article5518003.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sprek_snus"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/676951838c1a51d713262dae1d3bd06c10d75a08.jpg?5986c56c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Bruk snusfornuft n\u00e5r du trener -adressa.no", "St\u00f8rre risiko for skader", "Livsstilssykdommer", "Avhengigheten verst"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "676951838c1a51d713262dae1d3bd06c10d75a08"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["sport", "sprek"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["prosent menn", "bruk snusfornuft", "prosent kvinner", "snus", "\u00f8kt sjanse"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["innlandet", "statistisk", "norges idrettsforbund"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["danmark", "hamar"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "kjetil h\u00f8ye"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["sport", "spo